  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK641">
<l>nānala meṉṉu nalaṉuṭaimai yannalam </l>
<l>yānalat tuḷḷatūu maṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The possession of that goodness which is called the goodness of speech is (even to others) better than any other goodness.</l>
            </lg>
